LocPromotionPopupText = "Rend attacks that damage, but do not kill a living target still give a <font color='#3ABD23'><Ability:SOULBIND_FOCUS_CHANCE/>%</font> chance to transfer Energy to the <Ability:ClassName/>. Rend attacks that do kill a living target can regenerate <font color='#3ABD23'><Ability:SOULBIND_HP_HEALED/>HP</font> for the <Ability:ClassName/>.<br/><br/><Bullet/> HP cannot be regenerated and Energy cannot be harvested through Soulbind from mechanical enemies or zombies."

