LocLongDescription = "The <Ability:ClassName/> pours Energy into their Psi Blades, scaling up their Rend damage based on current Energy levels. Gain <font color='#3ABD23'>+<Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_DAMAGE_CHANCE/>%</font> chance to deal <font color='#3ABD23'>+<Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> Damage on all Psi Blade attacks for each unit of Energy stored, but the maximum amount of Energy the <Ability:ClassName/> can harness at any one time is reduced by <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_MAX_FOCUS_MODIFIER/></font>."
LocPromotionPopupText = "The <Ability:ClassName/> pours Energy into their Psi Blades, scaling up their Rend damage based on current Energy levels. Gain <font color='#3ABD23'>+<Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_DAMAGE_CHANCE/>%</font> chance to deal <font color='#3ABD23'>+<Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> Damage on all Psi Blade attacks for each unit of Energy stored, but the maximum amount of Energy the <Ability:ClassName/> can harness at any one time is reduced by <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_MAX_FOCUS_MODIFIER/></font>.<br/><br/><Bullet/> The chance to deal additional Damage stacks and rolls over: For example, having 150% chance would result in a guaranteed (100%) <font color='#3ABD23'>+<Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> Damage and a 50% chance to roll an additional <font color='#3ABD23'>+<Ability:CONSECRATED_BLADES_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> Damage.<br/><Bullet/> The bonus Damage from Consecrated Blades impacts direct Psi Blade attacks, such as Rend and Skyfall, as well as reaction attacks from Bladestorm.<br/><Bullet/> The bonus damage from Consecrated Blades only applies to the primary target, and does not affect any additional AOE targets from Arcwave, etc."

